---
title: Midweek Mexican Style Chorizo Pilaf with Bell Pepper and Soured Cream
description: On the table in less than 25 minutes, this Midweek Mexican Style Chorizo Pilaf is quick but still full of flavour. It combines the Indian technique of pilaf, a sautéed rice dish, with Mexican flavours from chipotle and cumin.
